content: harperaa: Merged two bug fix PRs this month, including PR #4537 addressing an error with TEXT_EMBEDDING (+32/-4 lines) and PR #4557 fixing the community manager to use plugin-local-ai out of the box (+1158/-519 lines). Contributed to discussions by commenting on 3 issues and 3 PRs. Activity was sporadic, concentrated on a single day during the month.
